trade_signal_metadata.name: Multi-Timeframe Liquidity Reversal Strategy v2.5
trade_signal_metadata.desc: This expert-level trading algorithm combines candle stick patterns with price action and momentum analysis to pinpoint liquidity exhaustion reversal zones across multiple timeframes. Utilizing the Liquidity Cluster indicator on 4-hour charts and institutional order blocks, this strategy aims to identify precise entry points on lower timeframes for maximum profit potential.
